    Get the latest Windows MIDI Services runtime and tools

    1.0 Customer Preview 3

    Download and install the MIDI 2.0 runtime for MIDI 2.0 applications, MIDI Settings app for creating loopback endpoints and customizing MIDI, management tools, PowerShell 7 cmdlets for MIDI, MIDI Console, and more, all in one package.

    About Windows MIDI Services

    Windows MIDI Services is an open source project, created by Microsoft, to update MIDI 1.0 and add MIDI 2.0 support to Windows.
